OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry in the east through the
OL,6,Fmorning with variable cloud and some
OL,7,Fbright spells possible. Cloud in the
OL,8,Fwest with the odd light shower
OL,9,Fpossible. Drier for a time around
OL,10,Flunchtime before outbreaks of rain
OL,11,Fspread east through the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will stay cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe evening and overnight with mainly
OL,15,Flight rain, but this will turn heavier
OL,16,Fand more persistent at times in the
OL,17,Fsouthwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
