OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy throughout the day
OL,6,Fand breezy at times. Outbreaks of
OL,7,Flight rain or drizzle will be patchy
OL,8,Fin the east, but persistent and heavy
OL,9,Fat times in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,12,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,13,Ffew days with spells of rain,
OL,14,Fpersistent at times in the west, but
OL,15,Fdrier in the east with some bright
OL,16,Fspells possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
